{"title":"VIIRS Net Primary Productivity Cloud Run Workflow","markdown":{"headingText":"VIIRS Net Primary Productivity Cloud Run Workflow","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\nThis chapter documents a cloud-based workflow for generating VIIRS net primary productivity products.\n\n## Purpose\n\nThis workflow computes daily and monthly satellite-derived primary productivity products from VIIRS inputs using a containerized Cloud Run Job pattern.\n\n## Repository structure\n\nThe workflow follows a consistent template: configuration, deployment assets, processing scripts, and NetCDF templates.\n\n```text\nNOAA20-netpp-CloudRun/\n├── config/\n│   ├── config.yml\n│   └── requirements.txt\n├── deploy_job.sh\n├── Dockerfile\n├── entrypoint.sh\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── control_viirs_netpp.py\n│   ├── make_viirs_netpp.py\n│   ├── control_viirs_netpp_monthly.py\n│   └── make_viirs_netpp_monthly.py\n└── templates/\n    ├── nasa_noaa20_4km.cdl\n    ├── nasa_noaa20_4km_month.cdl\n    ├── nasa_snpp_4km.cdl\n    └── nasa_snpp_4km_month.cdl\n```\n\n\n## Codebase {.unnumbered}\n\nThe workflow is structured into modular components that support configuration,\ndeployment, processing, and product generation.\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"file-grid\">\n\n<div class=\"file-card\">\n<h3>config/</h3>\n<p>Runtime configuration and Python environment.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/config/config.yml\">config.yml</a> — sensor, GCS, API, and processing settings</li>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/config/requirements.txt\">requirements.txt</a> — Python dependencies</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"file-card\">\n<h3>deployment files</h3>\n<p>Top-level files used to build and run the Cloud Run jobs.</p>\n<ul>\n<a href=\"code-pages/viirs-netpp/dockerfile.html\">Dockerfile</a>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/entrypoint.sh\">entrypoint.sh</a> — job mode selector</li>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/deploy_job.sh\">deploy_job.sh</a> — build, deploy, and schedule jobs</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"file-card\">\n<h3>scripts/</h3>\n<p>Processing and orchestration logic.</p>\n\n<h4>Daily products</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/scripts/control_viirs_netpp.py\">control_viirs_netpp.py</a> — daily run orchestrator</li>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/scripts/make_viirs_netpp.py\">make_viirs_netpp.py</a> — daily productivity generator</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Monthly composites</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/scripts/control_viirs_netpp_monthly.py\">control_viirs_netpp_monthly.py</a> — monthly run orchestrator</li>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/scripts/make_viirs_netpp_monthly.py\">make_viirs_netpp_monthly.py</a> — monthly composite builder</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"file-card\">\n<h3>templates/</h3>\n<p>CDL templates used to create NetCDF outputs.</p>\n\n<h4>NOAA-20</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/templates/nasa_noaa20_4km.cdl\">nasa_noaa20_4km.cdl</a> — daily template</li>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/templates/nasa_noaa20_4km_month.cdl\">nasa_noaa20_4km_month.cdl</a> — monthly template</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>SNPP</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/templates/nasa_snpp_4km.cdl\">nasa_snpp_4km.cdl</a> — daily template</li>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/templates/nasa_snpp_4km_month.cdl\">nasa_snpp_4km_month.cdl</a> — monthly template</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"file-card\">\n<h3>project metadata</h3>\n<p>Documentation, licensing, and change tracking.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/README.md\">README.md</a> — project overview</li>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/CHANGELOG.md\">CHANGELOG.md</a> — version history and workflow changes</li>\n<li><a href=\"workflows/viirs-netpp/LICENSE\">LICENSE</a> — license terms</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n</div>","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina",